<< 
DescPackaging: <<
Prevent configure scripts from confusing 10.10 (Yosemite) with 10.1 (Puma).

Upstream now uses -flat_namespace linkages to solve https://github.com/open-mpi/ompi/issues/259.
This causes Fink to produce "serious warning" messages about the use of -flat_namespace,
but these can be ignored.

Someone reported a build failure which was solved by using a single build job, so at least
for the time being use UMBJ: false:

https://sourceforge.net/p/fink/mailman/message/35902734/
<<
